* Rieger, Joerg and Kwok Pui-lan (2012). ''[https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=xBUQclqyE9cC Occupy Religion: Theology of the Multitude]''. Plymouth: Rowman & Littlefield Publishers. {{ISBN|978-1-442-21792-8}}.

